com.microsoft.bingads.v13.bulk.entities

Class BulkDynamicSearchAd

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.internal.bulk.BulkObject
      • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.bulk.entities.BulkEntity
        • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.internal.bulk.entities.SingleRecordBulkEntity
          • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.bulk.entities.BulkDynamicSearchAd

  • public class BulkDynamicSearchAd
extends SingleRecordBulkEntity
    Represents a dynamic search ad. This class exposes the #setDynamicSearchtAd and getDynamicSearchAd() methods that can be used to read and write fields of the Dynamic Search Ad record in a bulk file.

    For more information, see Dynamic Search Ad at https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=846127

    See Also:
    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter
